        <p>
            A sports car is designed to emphasise handling, performance or thrill of driving. Sports cars originated in Europe in the early 1900s
            and are currently produced by many manufacturers around the world.
        </p>
        <img src="https://images.wallpaperscraft.com/image/ferrari_red_cars_sport_95424_1280x720.jpg" width="128" height="72" />
